data.description: Just minutes from downtown, this adorable 2-bedroom, 1-bath home was recently remodeled in 2021 to include new exterior and interior paint, new vinyl windows, a new roof, new flooring, appliances, and more! Even better, this property is zoned for both commercial and residential use. Furthermore, it is located near many stores, restaurants, and more, offering a multitude of desirable options for however you choose to utilize the flexible zoning. Additionally, the 2-car detached garage is spacious and can serve as a great workshop, storage space, or more. With lots of potential and multipurpose zoning, you surely don't want to miss out on this unique opportunity. Schedule your private tour today!
